These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, motorbike
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
3. the person driving the skateboard is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the boat is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Transport    | boat    | motorbike | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
City: nizza, liverpool, boston
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| City       | liverpool | boston | nizza |
| Transport   | taxi    | roller     | boat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, water-polo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Sport         | water-polo     | rowing | ice-hockey |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
There 3 different types of food: banana, apricot, cucumber
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse
1. the person eating apricot is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person eating banana is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person eating apricot is in an even position##4
4. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Food   | cucumber | apricot  | banana  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, airplane, helicopter
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, dutch
1. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the tram and the canadian##2
2. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
3. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Transport         | tram   | helicopter | airplane    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch     | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
House: futuristic, modern, ranch-style
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the futuristic house is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the modern house##1
3. the modern house is in an odd position##4
4. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| House   | modern | ranch-style | futuristic   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

