.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, funk
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, dahlia, marigold
1. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | dubstep  | ambient  |
| Flower         | marigold | dahlia | iris |

