.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bolivar, game
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike
1. the game-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the person driving the trike is the game-smoker##1
4. the game-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Cigar         | bolivar | game | aristoff |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

