2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
4. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | spy     | romance |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water | juice    |

