2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Food          | watermelon | cucumber | kale  |
| Hobby   | skydiving      | board-games  | singing |

