.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, gardening, hiking
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta, iced-tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | hiking | camping   | gardening |
| Beverage   | fanta   | lemonade | iced-tea      |

