2. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Pet      | ferret | bird | horse |
| Nationality   | argentine   | thai          | american |

